            . I am an officer. I produce the thread.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. It is my thread and my partner's, I value it at two pound fifteen.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in her defence, nor called any witnesses to her character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 48.</p>
